00:13:21,474 --> 00:13:24,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>is attacking Gunma.</b></font>

158
00:13:24,584 --> 00:13:27,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've heard that, too.</b></font>

159
00:13:27,214 --> 00:13:29,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Everyone's talking about them.
--Yeah.</b></font>

160
00:13:29,884 --> 00:13:33,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I heard they cut the Night Kids' sticker in half</b></font>

161
00:13:33,054 --> 00:13:36,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and put it upside down
on one of their spoilers.</b></font>

162
00:13:36,554 --> 00:13:38,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Who would do such a thing?</b></font>

163
00:13:38,264 --> 00:13:41,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are they really coming here, too?</b></font>

164
00:13:41,264 --> 00:13:44,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What will you do if they come, Sayuki?</b></font>

165
00:13:44,264 --> 00:13:46,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's a stupid question.</b></font>

166
00:13:46,834 --> 00:13:49,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Isn't that right, Mako?</b></font>

167
00:13:49,334 --> 00:13:53,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Right. We'll take anyone's challenge</b></font>

168
00:13:53,104 --> 00:13:56,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>because we're Usui's fastest, "Impact Blue."</b></font>

169
00:13:58,244 --> 00:14:02,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's how we feel, so help us out, okay?</b></font>

170
00:14:02,384 --> 00:14:04,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The moment you see their Lan-Evos,</b></font>

171
00:14:04,884 --> 00:14:07,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>call me on my cell phone.</b></font>

172
00:14:07,384 --> 00:14:09,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

173
00:14:23,704 --> 00:14:27,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's been two days, but the Lan-Evo</i>
<i>Squad hasn't shown up yet.</i></b></font>

174
00:14:31,784 --> 00:14:36,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Maybe they're not coming to Usui.</i></b></font>

175
00:14:36,114 --> 00:14:39,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Part of me will feel relieved if they don't.</i></b></font>

176
00:14:42,954 --> 00:14:46,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I haven't been at the top of my game lately.</i></b></font>

177
00:14:46,794 --> 00:14:48,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>If I had to face them right now,</i></b></font>

178
00:14:48,794 --> 00:14:53,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm not sure I could run my best race.</i></b></font>

179
00:15:01,574 --> 00:15:07,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>But I do want to clear this haze from my mind.</i></b></font>

180
00:15:07,184 --> 00:15:10,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I want to forget about Iketani.</i></b></font>

181
00:15:11,484 --> 00:15:13,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Come on!!</b></font>

182
00:15:17,024 --> 00:15:18,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sayuki?!</b></font>

183
00:15:18,624 --> 00:15:22,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What are you doing in my bathroom?!</b></font>

184
00:15:22,034 --> 00:15:26,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This isn't the time for a relaxing bath, Mako!</b></font>

185
00:15:26,664 --> 00:15:28,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's going on?</b></font>

186
00:15:28,374 --> 00:15:31,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I came to pick you up! We're going.</b></font>

187
00:15:31,874 --> 00:15:33,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Going where?</b></font>

188
00:15:33,604 --> 00:15:35,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>To Usui Pass!</b></font>

189
00:15:35,274 --> 00:15:37,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Those Lan-Evos are here!</b></font>

190
00:15:41,314 --> 00:15:43,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just hurry up and put on your underwear.</b></font>

191
00:15:43,984 --> 00:15:45,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just give me a second!</b></font>

192
00:15:45,684 --> 00:15:47,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is embarrassing!</b></font>

193
00:16:07,204 --> 00:16:09,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Here come the Lan-Evos!</b></font>

194
00:16:16,084 --> 00:16:19,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's the Emperors, all right. They really came.</b></font>

195
00:16:19,754 --> 00:16:22,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Did you call Sayuki and Mako?
--Yeah.</b></font>

196
00:16:29,064 --> 00:16:32,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What? The Lan-Evos are there?</b></font>

197
00:16:32,064 --> 00:16:35,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, the Emperor guys you told me about.</b></font>

198
00:16:35,674 --> 00:16:38,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We're on our way there.</b></font>

199
00:16:38,874 --> 00:16:41,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Got it.</b></font>

200
00:16:41,014 --> 00:16:42,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takeshi!</b></font>

201
00:16:43,614 --> 00:16:46,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Lan-Evo Squad showed up in Usui.</b></font>

202
00:16:47,684 --> 00:16:49,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They did?</b></font>

203
00:16:49,714 --> 00:16:52,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's go, Takeshi.</b></font>

204
00:16:52,584 --> 00:16:54,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

205
00:17:13,374 --> 00:17:16,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I see nothing but FR drift punks here, too.</b></font>

206
00:17:16,574 --> 00:17:20,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I must say that Gunma's level is pretty low.</b></font>

207
00:17:20,544 --> 00:17:23,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's go back and tell Kyoichi about this.</b></font>

208
00:17:23,384 --> 00:17:24,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

209
00:17:59,454 --> 00:18:01,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, guys...</b></font>

210
00:18:01,454 --> 00:18:04,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you're here to race,
we'll take your challenge,</b></font>

211
00:18:04,354 --> 00:18:07,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>'cause our Sileighty is the fastest car around.</b></font>

212
00:18:13,504 --> 00:18:14,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Shingo...</b></font>

213
00:18:14,834 --> 00:18:19,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is anything going on between
you and that Sileighty girl?</b></font>

214
00:18:19,704 --> 00:18:21,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You mean Sayuki?</b></font>

215
00:18:21,944 --> 00:18:26,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We're just childhood friends, that's all.</b></font>

216
00:18:26,284 --> 00:18:31,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We lived close to each other
and went to the same school.</b></font>

217
00:18:32,684 --> 00:18:36,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--I see.
--Yeah.</b></font>

218
00:18:36,194 --> 00:18:37,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wait a minute, Takeshi.</b></font>

219
00:18:37,864 --> 00:18:41,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You like girls like that?</b></font>

220
00:18:41,194 --> 00:18:43,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well...</b></font>

221
00:18:43,394 --> 00:18:44,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You don't want her.</b></font>

222
00:18:44,704 --> 00:18:47,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>She's a strong-minded rebel.</b></font>

223
00:18:48,804 --> 00:18:52,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>She's not the kind of girl
who listens to anyone's advice,</b></font>

224
00:18:52,974 --> 00:18:56,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but even if they are the fastest in Usui,</b></font>

225
00:18:56,544 --> 00:18:59,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>they have no chance against those Lan-Evos.</b></font>

226
00:19:00,344 --> 00:19:04,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I admit that their drifting
technique is amazing.</b></font>

227
00:19:04,554 --> 00:19:08,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Maybe no one in Usui could touch them,</b></font>

228
00:19:08,394 --> 00:19:11,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but they have almost no
experience with pure speed racing--</b></font>

229
00:19:11,564 --> 00:19:14,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>the kind that requires remarkable control.</b></font>

230
00:19:14,694 --> 00:19:19,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I must say their control isn't crisp enough.</b></font>

231
00:19:19,834 --> 00:19:23,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They'll be outclassed by a serious 4WD car.</b></font>

232
00:19:24,944 --> 00:19:28,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know you know what
I'm talking about, Takeshi.</b></font>

233
00:19:31,444 --> 00:19:35,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't mean to say that they're
slow just because they're girls,</b></font>

234
00:19:35,614 --> 00:19:37,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but they have no chance.</b></font>

235
00:19:43,754 --> 00:19:46,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A Sileighty, huh?</b></font>

236
00:19:46,524 --> 00:19:48,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>With girl drivers.</b></font>

237
00:19:50,864 --> 00:19:53,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's play a little, 'cause this looks fun.</b></font>

238
00:19:53,704 --> 00:19:56,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, I don't know if that's a good idea.</b></font>

239
00:19:56,804 --> 00:19:58,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We're just scouting.</b></font>

240
00:19:58,644 --> 00:20:01,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You may get yelled at by Kyoichi later.</b></font>

241
00:20:01,574 --> 00:20:04,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't be such a tight-ass!</b></font>

242
00:20:04,744 --> 00:20:07,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We came all the way here.</b></font>

243
00:20:07,584 --> 00:20:11,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I see no harm in having a little fun.</b></font>

244
00:20:11,424 --> 00:20:13,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>As long as I win.</b></font>

245
00:20:13,584 --> 00:20:16,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But what if you lose to them?</b></font>

246
00:20:17,554 --> 00:20:21,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't insult me with your "what ifs," Ren.</b></font>

247
00:20:21,564 --> 00:20:24,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How could my Evo IV</b></font>

248
00:20:24,394 --> 00:20:27,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>lose to these bimbo drivers?</b></font>

249
00:20:28,604 --> 00:20:31,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hear that, Mako? That does it.</b></font>

250
00:20:31,404 --> 00:20:33,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He shouldn't have said that.</b></font>

251
00:20:33,574 --> 00:20:38,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>People who insult girl racers are the worst.</b></font>

252
00:20:38,114 --> 00:20:40,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Fine, I won't go easy on you.</b></font>

253
00:20:45,624 --> 00:20:47,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Her eyes are getting serious.</i></b></font>

254
00:20:47,924 --> 00:20:50,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>She's fast when she looks like that,</i></b></font>

255
00:20:50,094 --> 00:20:52,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>'cause her emotion is the fuel.</i></b></font>

256
00:21:03,804 --> 00:21:05,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is a downhill race.</b></font>

257
00:21:05,474 --> 00:21:09,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Since Usui Pass is narrow,
it'll be a "cat and mouse" race.</b></font>

258
00:21:09,474 --> 00:21:11,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If the mouse gets away, it's over.</b></font>

259
00:21:11,984 --> 00:21:16,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If not, we keep switching
positions until someone wins.</b></font>

260
00:21:16,514 --> 00:21:18,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you okay with that?</b></font>

261
00:21:18,324 --> 00:21:19,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's fine.</b></font>

262
00:21:19,984 --> 00:21:24,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Then go ahead and choose
which position you want first.</b></font>

263
00:21:24,694 --> 00:21:27,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll follow you first...</b></font>

264
00:21:27,694 --> 00:21:31,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...so I can check out your behind.</b></font>

265
00:21:31,194 --> 00:21:32,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's start, then.</b></font>

266
00:21:32,904 --> 00:21:37,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>After exiting the first corner,
we'll go full speed.</b></font>

267
00:21:37,574 --> 00:21:40,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's the start of the race. Got it?</b></font>

268
00:21:40,504 --> 00:21:42,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, okay.</b></font>

269
00:21:46,084 --> 00:21:48,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, are you gonna be okay?</b></font>

270
00:21:48,254 --> 00:21:50,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't make me repeat myself.</b></font>

271
00:21:50,554 --> 00:21:54,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm one of the top racers in the Emperors.</b></font>

272
00:21:54,924 --> 00:21:57,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm 200% sure that my Evo IV</b></font>

273
00:21:57,394 --> 00:22:01,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>won't lose to a Sileighty driven by two girls.</b></font>

274
00:22:09,034 --> 00:22:11,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's go!</b></font>

275
00:22:11,034 --> 00:22:15,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I refuse to lose to a guy
who insults girl racers.</b></font>

276
00:22:15,844 --> 00:22:19,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Mako, you look fired up.</b></font>

277
00:22:19,214 --> 00:22:21,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you ready, Sayuki?</b></font>

278
00:22:21,854 --> 00:22:23,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay.</b></font>

279
00:22:49,244 --> 00:22:50,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>An easy win.</b></font>

280
00:22:50,914 --> 00:22:55,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>His Evo IV can't possibly lose to a Sileighty.</b></font>

281
00:22:55,314 --> 00:22:57,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're really doing it.</b></font>

282
00:22:57,914 --> 00:23:01,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When it counts, women have more courage.</b></font>

283
00:23:01,594 --> 00:23:06,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Can they defeat the Emperors,
who defeated the Night Kids?</b></font>

284
00:23:06,424 --> 00:23:09,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That Evo IV is a high-powered 4WD car.</b></font>

285
00:23:09,894 --> 00:23:12,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anyone else would've run away.</b></font>

286
00:23:12,304 --> 00:23:15,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But if Sayuki and Mako can't beat that guy,</b></font>

287
00:23:15,174 --> 00:23:16,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>no one else can.</b></font>

288
00:23:16,974 --> 00:23:20,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Right. I don't know who
named them "Impact Blue,"</b></font>

289
00:23:20,004 --> 00:23:22,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but they're Usui's fastest.</b></font>

290
00:23:22,944 --> 00:23:27,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>All we can do is believe in them,
because Sayuki's blue Sileighty</b></font>

291
00:23:27,684 --> 00:23:29,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>is the best here.</b></font>

292
00:23:42,534 --> 00:23:44,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're not bad.</b></font>

293
00:23:44,364 --> 00:23:47,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is their course, so they
know how to attack it.</b></font>

294
00:23:50,504 --> 00:23:53,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No cars ahead. Drift right through here!</b></font>

295
00:24:01,554 --> 00:24:06,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My Evo I V's drift is far better</i>
<i>than an FR's pitiful drift.</i></b></font>

296
00:24:06,124 --> 00:24:08,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's a high-speed 4WD drift</i></b></font>

297
00:24:08,954 --> 00:24:11,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>with the engine full blast!</i></b></font>

298
00:24:23,504 --> 00:24:25,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Mako, you're doing great.</b></font>

299
00:24:25,344 --> 00:24:29,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Grip the next corner and hug the inner wall!</b></font>

300
00:24:36,654 --> 00:24:39,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We're about even so far.</b></font>

301
00:24:39,354 --> 00:24:42,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm not sure if it's the Evo IV itself</b></font>

302
00:24:42,394 --> 00:24:46,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>or the driver's technique that's
letting him keep up with us.</b></font>

303
00:24:51,334 --> 00:24:53,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Like you said,</b></font>

304
00:24:53,364 --> 00:24:57,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>swinging drift involves many variables.</b></font>

305
00:24:57,334 --> 00:24:59,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It all depends on how you use the tires.</b></font>

306
00:24:59,344 --> 00:25:01,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

307
00:25:01,744 --> 00:25:05,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When was the last time
you saw this Sileighty race?</b></font>

308
00:25:05,714 --> 00:25:07,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sometime last spring.</b></font>

309
00:25:07,714 --> 00:25:10,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Then she may have changed.</b></font>

310
00:25:11,854 --> 00:25:14,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've experienced it, too.</b></font>

311
00:25:14,124 --> 00:25:17,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>After a painful loss,</b></font>

312
00:25:17,624 --> 00:25:21,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>a talented racer can change big-time.</b></font>

313
00:25:21,294 --> 00:25:23,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

314
00:25:23,064 --> 00:25:25,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There are talented FR racers</b></font>

315
00:25:25,864 --> 00:25:28,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>like Akina's Eight-Six in this world.</b></font>

316
00:25:28,934 --> 00:25:32,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There is an FR racer who can beat a 4WD car.</b></font>

317
00:25:32,374 --> 00:25:35,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But that Eight-Six is an exception.</b></font>

318
00:25:35,874 --> 00:25:39,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I guess it would've been a different story</b></font>

319
00:25:39,544 --> 00:25:43,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>if those girls had ever had a
chance to see that Eight-Six race.</b></font>

320
00:25:55,164 --> 00:26:00,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hmph, insolent chick drivers!</b></font>

321
00:26:00,234 --> 00:26:02,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I won't lose, no matter what!</i></b></font>

322
00:26:05,844 --> 00:26:09,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Amazing! Her driving is totally different.</i></b></font>

323
00:26:10,174 --> 00:26:13,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Her steering has definitely gotten tighter.</i></b></font>

324
00:26:15,254 --> 00:26:18,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Her driving probably got this way</i></b></font>

325
00:26:18,254 --> 00:26:20,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>after the race against Akina's Eight-Six.</i></b></font>

326
00:26:34,704 --> 00:26:36,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Mako has woken up!</i></b></font>

327
00:26:36,204 --> 00:26:39,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You're amazing, Mako! We can win this race!</i></b></font>

328
00:26:57,194 --> 00:27:00,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That Evo I Visn't as sharp at the corners.</i></b></font>

329
00:27:02,534 --> 00:27:05,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He's not as great as I thought he was.</i></b></font>

330
00:27:05,004 --> 00:27:08,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He's probably not the one who</i>
<i>defeated the Night Kids in Myogi.</i></b></font>

331
00:27:12,374 --> 00:27:16,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>In that case, I hate to keep</i>
<i>showing him our behinds.</i></b></font>

332
00:27:16,814 --> 00:27:20,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We'll finish him at the next corner, C-121!</b></font>

333
00:27:22,714 --> 00:27:24,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know you know this,</b></font>

334
00:27:24,314 --> 00:27:27,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but you're much faster on
the straightaways tonight.</b></font>

335
00:27:27,054 --> 00:27:30,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You'll be entering the
corner at a higher speed,</b></font>

336
00:27:30,394 --> 00:27:33,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so don't forget to adjust for that!</b></font>

337
00:27:39,204 --> 00:27:42,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Good, no cars ahead. Go!</b></font>

338
00:27:52,214 --> 00:27:54,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If those girls can clear this corner,</b></font>

339
00:27:54,944 --> 00:27:57,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>my Evo IV certainly can!</b></font>

340
00:28:15,374 --> 00:28:17,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm going wide!</i></b></font>

341
00:28:17,304 --> 00:28:19,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I can't stay on the same line!</i></b></font>

342
00:28:35,424 --> 00:28:37,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's over, Mako.</b></font>

343
00:28:49,304 --> 00:28:52,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, are you okay?</b></font>

344
00:28:52,344 --> 00:28:54,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

345
00:28:54,744 --> 00:29:00,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, don't tell Kyoichi
anything about this, okay?</b></font>

346
00:29:00,184 --> 00:29:01,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sure.</b></font>

347
00:29:15,834 --> 00:29:18,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sayuki, where's the Lan-Evo Squad?</b></font>

348
00:29:22,674 --> 00:29:24,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're late, Shingo.</b></font>

349
00:29:24,504 --> 00:29:26,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We're already done.</b></font>

350
00:29:26,874 --> 00:29:30,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What? It's over?</b></font>

351
00:29:30,374 --> 00:29:33,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I see. Don't be discouraged.</b></font>

352
00:29:33,714 --> 00:29:37,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We lost on our home turf, too.</b></font>

353
00:29:37,314 --> 00:29:39,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What are you talking about?!</b></font>

354
00:29:39,224 --> 00:29:40,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We won.</b></font>

355
00:29:43,124 --> 00:29:45,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I said we won.</b></font>

356
00:29:50,494 --> 00:29:52,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They won?!</b></font>

357
00:29:54,364 --> 00:29:56,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Mako was amazing.</b></font>

358
00:29:56,334 --> 00:29:59,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>She's a genius.</b></font>

359
00:29:59,044 --> 00:30:00,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't tease.</b></font>

360
00:30:02,014 --> 00:30:04,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's go home.</b></font>

361
00:30:05,384 --> 00:30:07,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>See ya, Shingo.</b></font>

362
00:30:12,224 --> 00:30:16,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, we came out here to root for you.</b></font>

363
00:30:24,864 --> 00:30:28,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That Sileighty is giving off a blinding aura.</b></font>

364
00:30:28,904 --> 00:30:31,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're the real thing!</b></font>

365
00:30:48,754 --> 00:30:50,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're amazing, Mako.</b></font>

366
00:30:50,954 --> 00:30:55,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Maybe last night's Lan-Evo wasn't that good.</b></font>

367
00:30:55,264 --> 00:30:56,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's not true.</b></font>

368
00:30:56,594 --> 00:30:59,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He was pretty good.</b></font>

369
00:30:59,764 --> 00:31:01,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It would've been a tough race</b></font>

370
00:31:01,604 --> 00:31:05,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>had we raced him before
we raced Akina's Eight-Six.</b></font>

371
00:31:05,374 --> 00:31:09,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Less-angled cornering has
been our focus since our loss,</b></font>

372
00:31:09,614 --> 00:31:12,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and you executed it perfectly.</b></font>

373
00:31:18,214 --> 00:31:22,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But at C-121, when we went for the kill,</b></font>

374
00:31:22,054 --> 00:31:26,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>you went back to your flashy, dramatic drift.</b></font>

375
00:31:26,294 --> 00:31:30,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I guess I entered that corner way too fast.</b></font>

376
00:31:30,064 --> 00:31:33,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I get scared thinking about it now.</b></font>

377
00:31:34,064 --> 00:31:36,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It wasn't funny last night.</b></font>

378
00:31:36,574 --> 00:31:38,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I thought I was gonna die.</b></font>

379
00:31:38,504 --> 00:31:42,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You sure are an emotional racer.</b></font>

380
00:31:42,344 --> 00:31:45,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You suddenly change into someone else.</b></font>

381
00:31:48,144 --> 00:31:51,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I feel kind of relieved now.</b></font>

382
00:31:56,654 --> 00:32:00,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But I still have a long way to go.</b></font>

383
00:32:00,664 --> 00:32:05,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I feel like I'm chasing after something
that's beyond that blue sky.</b></font>

384
00:32:07,804 --> 00:32:10,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't need a man for a while.</b></font>

385
00:32:11,304 --> 00:32:13,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just watch me, Iketani!</b></font>

386
00:32:15,144 --> 00:32:16,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Bang!</b></font>

387
00:32:18,844 --> 00:32:23,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Have you caught a cold, Iketani?</b></font>

388
00:32:23,214 --> 00:32:24,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, I don't think so.</b></font>

389
00:32:25,824 --> 00:32:28,814
